    dc:description "Figure 4. Digital Photo-illustration. Habitus, dorsal aspect. A Hyboptera tiputini Erwin & Henry, sp. n., male, ADP 135850 B Hyboptera viridivittis Chaudoir, male, ADP 007599." ;
